question: What is the average number of tickets sold per event in each quarter of the year?
sql:
SELECT 
    c.CATNAME, 
    SUM(s.PRICEPAID) AS TOTAL_REVENUE
FROM 
    SALES s
JOIN 
    EVENT e ON s.EVENTID = e.EVENTID
JOIN 
    CATEGORY c ON e.CATID = c.CATID
JOIN 
    DATE d ON s.DATEID = d.DATEID
WHERE 
    d.YEAR = 2008
GROUP BY 
    c.CATNAME;
